**Objective:** Review and enhance UI/UX for high-traffic files: `client/src/pages/landing.tsx` and `client/src/pages/member-dashboard.tsx`. The focus is on aesthetic enhancements, interactive flows, and modern design principles to ensure an engaging and intuitive user experience.


